channel.title: [Delta] sendQuest question
channel.description:
How do I find certain sendQuest id's?
Any help or guidance towards the correct path is much appreciated. Thanks.
[b]Example.[/b] sendQuest("blah, blah", xxxx) - xxxx being, the id.
